nasty-proxmox-plugin (0.1.3) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Update storage API compatibility to PVE API level 14.
  * Fix NVMe device discovery: use NSID-based sysfs lookup instead of device path matching.
  * Fix taint-mode crash in _iscsi_remove_scsi_device: untaint readlink() result before use in open().
  * Fix WebSocket stale-connection failure after forked child exits: retry _api_call once on connection errors.
  * Fix NVMe idempotent activation by detecting an already-live controller before nvme connect.
  * Fix NVMe live migration by passing a deterministic hostid derived from the NASty hostnqn.

 -- NastyPlugin Maintainers <noreply@github.com>  Sun, 01 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000

