nasty-proxmox-plugin (0.1.1) bookworm; urgency=medium

  * Add Proxmox storage API compatibility declaration for PVE 8/9 loading.
  * Fix WebSocket response handling for auth broadcasts and event frames.
  * Use flat NASty block subvolume names accepted by the appliance API.
  * Encode allocate and resize byte counts as JSON numbers.
  * Return snapshot info in the shape expected by current Proxmox wrappers.
  * Ensure iSCSI login before path resolution and suppress iscsiadm stdout.
  * Update the full-function test script for current Proxmox CLI behavior.
  * Expand the NASty full-function test script to mirror TrueNAS plugin test coverage with NASty-specific checks.
  * Optimize full-function test pre-flight cleanup to avoid silent per-VMID storage scans.
  * Fix full-function test failure accounting so error logging cannot break shell returns.
  * Fix volume_size_info scalar-context return for Proxmox 9 disk attachment and resize validation.
  * Advertise snapshot/clone/copy feature support to Proxmox and untaint device paths for LXC rootfs formatting.
  * Fix full-function test NASty API helper JSON parameter handling and single-phase reruns.

 -- NastyPlugin Maintainers <noreply@github.com>  Sun, 31 May 2026 00:00:00 +0000

